
Install python

Install pip -
sudo apt install python3-pip
sudo apt install python3-testresources

Install following python libraries
pip install bacpypes==0.18.0


Run simulator

python3 bacnet_ip_device.py ip-address

E.g.
python3 bacnet_ip_device.py 192.168.1.110

For using different device name and port
python3 bacnet_ip_device.py 192.168.1.110 102 47809